# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# MCCIA Intern OS — environment configuration
#
# The app is currently fully client-side (data in the browser's localStorage),
# so NO environment variables are required to run it.
#
#   npm install && npm run dev
#
# This file is a placeholder for the planned Neon (Postgres) backend. When that
# lands, copy it to `.env.local` (gitignored — never commit real credentials)
# and fill in the connection string, e.g.:
#
#   # DATABASE_URL=postgres://user:password@host/db?sslmode=require
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
